#: src/kdefrontend/datasources/ImportFileWidget.cpp:197
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Specify how the data source has to be processed on every read:"
"<ul><li>Continuously fixed - fixed amount of samples is processed starting "
"from the beginning of the newly received data.</li><li>From End - fixed "
"amount of samples is processed starting from the end of the newly received "
"data.</li><li>Till the End - all newly received data is processed.</"
"li><li>Whole file - on every read the whole file is re-read completely and "
"processed. Only available for \"File Or Named Pipe\" data sources.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"Sonraigh conas is gá an fhoinse sonraí a phróiseáil ar gach léamh:<ul><li>Go "
"leanúnach socraithe - próiseáiltear líon socraithe samplaí ag tosú ó thús na "
"sonraí nua-fhaighte.</li><li>Ó Dheireadh - próiseáiltear líon socraithe "
"samplaí ag tosú ó dheireadh na sonraí nua-fhaighte.</li><li>Go dtí an "
"Deireadh - próiseáiltear na sonraí nua-fhaighte go léir.</li><li>Comhad "
"iomlán - ar gach léamh, athléítear an comhad iomlán go hiomlán agus "
"próiseáiltear é. Ar fáil do fhoinsí sonraí \"Comhad Nó Píopa Ainmnithe\" "
"amháin.</li></ul>"

#: src/kdefrontend/datasources/ImportFileWidget.cpp:208
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Number of samples (lines) to be processed on every read.\n"
"Only needs to be specified for the reading mode \"Continuously Fixed\" and "
"\"From End\"."
msgstr ""
"Líon na samplaí (línte) le próiseáil ar gach léamh.\n"
"Ní gá ach é a shonrú don mhodh léitheoireachta \"Seasta go Leanúnach\" agus "
"\"Ó Dheireadh\"."

#: src/kdefrontend/datasources/ImportFileWidget.cpp:214
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Specify when and how frequently the data source needs to be read:"
"<ul><li>Periodically - the data source is read periodically with user "
"specified time interval.</li><li>On New Data - the data source is read when "
"new data arrives.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"Sonraigh cathain agus cé chomh minic is gá an fhoinse sonraí a léamh:"
"<ul><li>Go tréimhsiúil - léitear an fhoinse sonraí go tréimhsiúil laistigh "
"den eatramh ama a shonraíonn an t-úsáideoir.</li><li>Ar Shonraí Nua - "
"léitear an fhoinse sonraí nuair a thagann sonraí nua.</li></ul>"

